Selig Rejects Los Angeles Dodgers’ Deal With Fox Linked to McCourt Divorce

-- B y   C u r t i s   E i c h e l b e r g e r
-- 
2011-06-20T20:59:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-20/selig-rejects-los-angeles-dodgers-deal-with-fox-linked-to-mccourt-divorce.html
Baseball Commissioner  Bud Selig 
rejected a proposed media-rights deal between  News Corp. (NWSA) ’s Fox
and the  Los Angeles Dodgers , an agreement at the heart of a
divorce settlement involving team owner  Frank McCourt  and his
ex-wife, Jamie.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
